                    <section class="six">
                        <div class="text-six">
                            <h2>4. Reports and analytics</h2>
                            <h3><br>How do you know if your office automation is yielding results? You can’t just evaluate process performance based
                                 on how happy your team is. Data is the ultimate decision-maker, and it’s important for your business to compare a process’
                                  history, its speed, the outcome quality, etc.</h3>
                                  <h3><br>Adopting another software to measure your workflow data is time-consuming and unnecessary. Why not have a single piece
                                     of software that comes embedded with reporting and analytics features? The best office automation products now come equipped
                                      with this feature as part of their fundamental offering.</h3>
                </section>
